---
title: Lemon Caper Scallops with Chive Orzo
description: It's date night and we're bringing our best flavours! A burst of briny capers pairs perfectly with butter-braised scallops for a true special occasion meal. Even the sides tonight are drool-worthy: Roasted cherry tomatoes and green beans bring a pop of brightness, alongside perfectly al dente, chive-studded orzo pasta.
